{"tid":1466310,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【勿被轉移視線】當前要務係必須立即啟動文宣機器，割唔割唔係重點","createTime":"2019-08-13T16:39:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T17:05:05.000Z","uid":55598,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f4e8d5e68268129aa7fb43a740c8f4d04b4d11b1","tid":1466310,"uid":55598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:39:49.000Z","msg":"而家大家已經被spin 到割唔割席或者係度互屌<br />\n呢啲討論喺呢一刻<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">完全幫唔到成個運動</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">如果想幫到件事，必須立即啟動海嘯級嘅文宣，重申林鄭政府漠視訴求同警察不斷濫暴先係根源！！！勿被轉移視線</span></span><br />\n<br />\n你見每次大野，對家必然立即製造大量fake news，比我哋仲快宣傳開去<br />\n<br />\n612，721，811 必須不斷重提，唔講呢三日，有邊一次黑警暴力係弱過今日？無！<br />\n<br />\n以及最重要：警方於前線扮示威者煽動暴力，不排除今日全部係警察煽動嘅可能性！警方刻意製造混亂！同埋捉到兩個公安有武器，更加真實中港合作！防暴講普通話嗰啲！全部要文宣！！！！！！！！！！！！！<br />\n<br />\n記住，我哋必須揸住呢一個盾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3701e197c34090192cda4b961611d3bb56238fed","tid":1466310,"uid":55598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:41:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cc790c5707e10353e4c3fb6ff8b9a5c46ea18549","tid":1466310,"uid":55598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:41:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4bf052220bd5bc027ef90d078fb2212a40f5199c","tid":1466310,"uid":55598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:42:29.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"4f81c6bf39677b612c74ab5ee14a4547e3f1370b","tid":1466310,"uid":55598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:43:26.000Z","msg":"推呀推上去呀"},{"pid":"be44312999ef0578a7c4f42c2726896124685816","tid":1466310,"uid":48277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:43:40.000Z","msg":"「唔完美，可接受，但需要改善、改進。」"},{"pid":"d128650c36d93f3bba8489a7d963d519e1c5389c","tid":1466310,"uid":55598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:44:33.000Z","ms